    <project id="powerplant_android">
        <name>Power plant android demo</name>
        <description>Kaa power plant demo for Android</description>
        <details>
            <![CDATA[
<h2>Installation</h2>
Download the .apk to your Android device by clicking the "Binary" button on the left. Make sure that the device permits installing apps from "Unknown sources". Open the downloaded apk and follow the on-screen instructions.

<h2>What's next?</h2>
Get the source code by clicking the "Source" button on the left and start hacking!<br/><br/>

For more background on user verification refer to the corresponding <a href="http://docs.kaaproject.org/display/KAA/Attaching+endpoints+to+users#Attachingendpointstousers-Userverifiers">design reference</a> section. It is also possible to implement custom user verifier using <a href="http://docs.kaaproject.org/display/KAA/Creating+custom+user+verifier">programming guide</a>.
            ]]>
        </details>
        
